	<row id="narc_0587_00273" index="273">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Et selvhelbredende træk.\nBrugeren gendanner sin\nuværende HP med op til halvdelen\naf dens maksimale HP\ni næste tur.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00274" index="274">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren skynder sig\nog bruger tilfældigt en\nbevægelse blandt dem\nkendt af andre\nPokémon i partiet.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00275" index="275">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren lægger rødder\nder genskaber HP hver gang.\nFordi den er rodfæstet,\nkan ikke skifte ud.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00276" index="276">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren angriber fjenden med stor kraft.\nDet sænker dog også\nbrugerens\nangreb og forsvar.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00277" index="277">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">En barriere afspejler\ntilbage til fjenden\nbevægelser som Leech\nSeed og bevægelser\nden skadestatus.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00278" index="278">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user recycles a\nsingle-use item that\nhas been used in\nbattle so it can be\nused again.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00279" index="279">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Et angrebstræk, der\npåfører den dobbelte\ndaskade, hvis brugeren\ner blevet såret af\nfjenden i samme tur.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00280" index="280">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user attacks with\ntough fists, etc. It\ncan also break any\nbarrier such as Light\nScreen and Reflect.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00281" index="281">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren slipper et\nstort gab, der får fjenden til at falde\n i søvn ved næste\ndrejning.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00282" index="282">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren smækker\nfjendens fastholdte genstand,\nforhindrer genstanden\ni at blive brugt\nunder kampen.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00283" index="283">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Et angrebstræk, der\nskærer fjendens\nHP ned, så det svarer til\brugerens HP.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00284" index="284">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren angriber i\n eksplosiv raseri.\nJo lavere brugerens\nHP, jo mindre kraftfuld\n bliver dette angreb.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00285" index="285">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren bruger sin\npsykiske kraft til at\nudveksle evner\nmed fjenden.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00286" index="286">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis fjenden kender nogen\nbevægelser, som også er kendt af\nbrugeren, er fjenden\n forhindret i at bruge den.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00287" index="287">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user rests\nto cure itself of a\npoisoning, burn, or\nparalysis.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00288" index="288">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis brugeren besvimer, \nbrugerens nag\nfjerner fuldstændigt PP'en\naf fjendens træk\nder slog den ud.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00289" index="289">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren stjæler\neffekterne af enhver\nhelbredelse eller status-\nændring af bevægelse fjenden\forsøg at bruge.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00290" index="290">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user attacks with\na secret power. Its\nadded effects vary\ndepending on the\nuser’s environment.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00291" index="291">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Et to-drejningsangreb.\nBrugeren dykker\nunder vandet i\nførste sving og rammer derefter\nnæste sving.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00292" index="292">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user looses a\nflurry of open-palmed\narm thrusts that hit\ntwo to five times in a\nrow.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00293" index="293">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user’s type is\nchanged depending on\nits environment, such\nas at water’s edge, in\ngrass, or in a cave.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00294" index="294">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user stares at\nflashing lights to\nfocus its mind,\nsharply raising its\nSp. Atk stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00295" index="295">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren mister en\nskadelig udbrud af\nlys. Det kan også\nreducere målets\nSp. Def stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00296" index="296">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">En tågelignende byge af\ndun omslutter og\nbeskadiger fjenden. Det\nkan også sænke\nmålets Sp. Atk.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00297" index="297">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren dækker\nfjenden med en masse\nned, der kraftigt\nsænker angrebsstaten.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00298" index="298">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user performs a\nwobbly dance that\nconfuses all the\nPokémon in battle.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00299" index="299">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user launches a\nkick with a high\ncritical-hit ratio.\nIt may also leave the\ntarget with a burn.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00300" index="300">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren dækker sig til med mudder. Det\nsvækker elektriske bevægelser, mens\nbrugeren er i kampen.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00301" index="301">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren ruller konstant\n ind i fjenden\nover fem omgange. Den\nbliver stærkere\nhver gang den rammer.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00302" index="302">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user attacks by\nwildly swinging its\nthorny arms.\nIt may also make the\ntarget flinch.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00303" index="303">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user slacks off,\nrestoring its own HP\nby up to half of its\nmaximum HP.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00304" index="304">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user lets loose\na horribly echoing\nshout with the\npower to inflict\ndamage.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00305" index="305">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user bites the\nfoe with toxic fangs.\nIt may also leave the\nfoe badly poisoned.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00306" index="306">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user slashes the\nfoe with hard and\nsharp claws.\nIt may also lower the\ntarget’s Defense.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00307" index="307">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Fjenden raseres af\n en flammende eksplosion.\nBrugeren skal dog hvile\nikke næste tur.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00308" index="308">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Fjenden bliver ramt med\n vandet eksplosion.\nBrugeren skal dog hvile\nikke næste sving.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00309" index="309">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Fjenden bliver ramt med et\nhårdt slag\nsom en meteor.\nDet kan også hæve\nbrugerens angreb.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00310" index="310">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user attacks the\nfoe while shouting in\na startling fashion.\nIt may also make the\ntarget flinch.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00311" index="311">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">An attack move that\nvaries in power and\ntype depending on\nthe weather.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00312" index="312">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user releases a\nsoothing scent that\nheals all status\nproblems affecting\nthe user’s party.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00313" index="313">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user feigns\ncrying to make the\nfoe feel flustered,\nsharply lowering its\nSp. Def stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00314" index="314">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren starter\nbarberlignende vind for at\nslashe fjenden.\nDen har et højt\nkritisk hit-forhold.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00315" index="315">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user attacks the\nfoe at full power.\nThe attack’s recoil\nsharply reduces the\nuser’s Sp. Atk stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00316" index="316">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Gør det muligt for brugeren at\nhitte en spøgelsestype med\nhver form for bevægelse. Det giver også brugeren\n mulighed for at ramme en undvigende fjende.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00317" index="317">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Kampesten kastes\nat fjenden. Det sænker også fjendens\nhastighed ved at forhindre\nens bevægelse.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00318" index="318">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The foe is attacked\nwith powdery scales\nblown by wind.\nIt may also raise all\nthe user’s stats.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00319" index="319">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">En forfærdelig lyd som\nskraber metal udsendes for skarpt\nreducere fjendens\nSp. Def stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00320" index="320">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren spiller en\nbehagelig melodi, der\nl får fjenden ind i\ndyb søvn.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00321" index="321">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user tickles the\nfoe into laughing,\nreducing its Attack\nand Defense stats.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00322" index="322">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user absorbs a\nmystical power from\nspace to raise its\nDefense and Sp. Def\nstats.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00323" index="323">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren sprøjter\nvand for at beskadige\nfjenden. Jo lavere\brugerens HP, jo mindre\nkraftfuld bliver den.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00324" index="324">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren angriber med\n uhyggelig stråle\nlys. Det kan også\nforvirre målet.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00325" index="325">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren kaster et\nslag mod fjenden fra\nskyggerne.\nPunchet lander\nuden fejl.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00326" index="326">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user attacks with\nan odd, unseeable\npower.\nIt may also make the\nfoe flinch.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00327" index="327">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user attacks the\nfoe with an uppercut\nthrown skyward\nwith force.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00328" index="328">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user traps the\nfoe inside a harshly\nraging sandstorm for\ntwo to five turns.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00329" index="329">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The foe is attacked\nwith a blast of\nabsolute-zero cold.\nThe foe instantly\nfaints if it hits.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00330" index="330">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user attacks by\nshooting out muddy\nwater.\nIt may also lower the\nfoe’s accuracy.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00331" index="331">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user forcefully\nshoots seeds at the\nfoe. Two to five\nseeds are shot in\nrapid succession.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00332" index="332">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user confounds\nthe foe with speed,\nthen slashes.\nThe attack lands\nwithout fail.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00333" index="333">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user launches\nsharp icicles at the\nfoe. It strikes two\nto five times in a\nrow.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00334" index="334">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user hardens\nits body’s surface\nlike iron, sharply\nraising its Defense\nstat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00335" index="335">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user blocks the\nfoe’s way with arms\nspread wide to\nprevent escape.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00336" index="336">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user howls loudly\nto raise its spirit,\nboosting its Attack\nstat.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00337" index="337">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user slashes the\nfoe with huge, sharp\nclaws.\n\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00338" index="338">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Fjenden bliver smækket\nmed et enormt\ntræ.\nBrugeren kan ikke bevæge sig\nden næste tur.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00339" index="339">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user tenses its\nmuscles to bulk up\nits body, boosting\nboth its Attack and\nDefense stats.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00340" index="340">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren hopper op\nhøjt og falder derefter på\nfjenden ved den anden\ndrejning. Det kan også\nlamme fjenden.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00341" index="341">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren angriber ved at\nslynge en klat mudder\nat fjenden.\nDet reducerer også\nmålets hastighed.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00342" index="342">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Et angreb med et\nhøjt kritisk hit\nforhold. Dette haleangreb kan også \nforgifte fjenden.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00343" index="343">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren nærmer sig kærligt\nfjenden,\nstjæler derefter genstanden\nfjenden holder.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00344" index="344">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren elektrificerer\nselv og oplader derefter fjenden. Det forårsager også\nbetydelig skade\nfor brugeren.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00345" index="345">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren spreder\nnysgerrige blade, der\njager fjenden.\nDette angreb vil ikke\ngå glip af.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00346" index="346">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren gennemvæder sig\nmed vand. Trækket\nsvækker Fire-type\nbevægelser, mens brugeren\n er i kampen.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00347" index="347">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user quietly\nfocuses its mind and\ncalms its spirit to\nraise its Sp. Atk and\nSp. Def stats.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00348" index="348">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The foe is slashed\nwith a sharp leaf.\nIt has a high\ncritical-hit ratio.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00349" index="349">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user vigorously\nperforms a mystic,\npowerful dance that\nboosts its Attack and\nSpeed stats.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00350" index="350">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren kaster hårde\nsten mod fjenden.\nTo til fem sten bliver\nlanceret i hurtig\nfølge.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00351" index="351">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren slår\nfjenden med et hurtigt stød\naf elektricitet.\nDette angreb kan ikke\nundgås.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00352" index="352">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user attacks the\nfoe with a pulsing\nblast of water.\nIt may also confuse\nthe foe.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00353" index="353">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">To omgange efter dette\ntræk er brugt, blæser\nbrugeren fjenden\nmed et koncentreret\nbundt lys.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00354" index="354">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user attacks the\nfoe at full power.\nThe attack’s recoil\nsharply reduces the\nuser’s Sp. Atk stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00355" index="355">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user lands and\nrests its body.\nIt restores the\nuser’s HP by up to\nhalf of its max HP.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00356" index="356">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Gravity is intensified\nfor five turns, making\nmoves involving flying\nunusable and\nnegating Levitation.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00357" index="357">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Gør det muligt for brugeren at\nhitte en spøgelsestype med\nhver form for bevægelse. Det giver også brugeren\n mulighed for at ramme en undvigende fjende.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00358" index="358">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Dette angreb påfører\nstor skade på en sovende fjende. Det vækker dog også fjenden\n.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00359" index="359">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren svinger og\nslår med sin stærke\ntunge knytnæve.\nDet sænker dog brugerens\nhastighed.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00360" index="360">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren tackler\nfjenden med et højhastigheds\nspin. Jo langsommere\brugeren, jo større\nskaden.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00361" index="361">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren besvimer. Tilbage vil den Pokémon\n, der indtager sin plads,\nfå sin HP gendannet\nog status helbredt.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00362" index="362">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis fjendens HP er\nned til omkring det halve,\nvil dette angreb ramme\nmed dobbelt\nkraft.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00363" index="363">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user draws power\nto attack by using\nits held Berry.\nThe Berry determines\nits type and power.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00364" index="364">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">An attack that hits a\nfoe using Protect or\nDetect. It also lifts\nthe effects of those\nmoves.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00365" index="365">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren hakker fjenden. Hvis fjenden\nholder en bær, plukker\brugeren den og\nvinder dens effekt.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00366" index="366">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren fremkalder en\nturbulent hvirvelvind\nder øger hastigheden\nfor alle parters Pokémon\ni tre omgange.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00367" index="367">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user applies\npressure to stress\npoints, sharply\nboosting one of its\nstats.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00368" index="368">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren gengælder\nmod fjenden, der\nsidst har påført skade\nden med meget\nstørre kraft.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00369" index="369">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Efter at have foretaget sit\angreb, skynder brugeren sig tilbage for at skifte\nplads med en fest\nPokémon i vente.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00370" index="370">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren bekæmper fjenden tæt uden\n at beskytte sig selv. Det skærer også brugerens\nForsvar og Sp. Def.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00371" index="371">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis brugeren kan bruge\ndette angreb efter\nfjendens angreb, fordobles dets\nkraft.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00372" index="372">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis fjenden\nallerede har taget noget\nskade i samme\ndrejning, fordobles dette angrebs\nkraft.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00373" index="373">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Det forhindrer fjenden\ni at bruge sit holdt\nem. Dens træner er også forhindret i at\bruge genstande på den.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00374" index="374">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren kaster sin\nholdte genstand mod fjenden\nfor at angribe. Dens kraft\nog effekter afhænger\n af emnet.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00375" index="375">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Ved at bruge sin psykiske\nkraft af forslag,\noverfører brugeren\n sine statusproblemer\ntil målet.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00376" index="376">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Jo færre PP dette\ntræk har, jo mere\nkraft har det til\angreb.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00377" index="377">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user prevents\nthe foe from using\nany HP-recovery\nmoves for five turns.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00378" index="378">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren vrider fjenden kraftigt\n.\nJo mere HP fjenden\nhar, jo større magt er dette angreb.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00379" index="379">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user employs its\npsychic power to\nswitch its Attack\nwith its Defense\nstat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00380" index="380">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren kaster sine\nmavesyrer op på\nfjenden. Væsken\neliminerer effekten\naf fjendens evner.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00381" index="381">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user chants an\nincantation toward\nthe sky, preventing\nthe foe from landing\ncritical hits.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00382" index="382">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren forsøger at skære\n foran fjenden for at\nstjæle og bruge\nfjendens tilsigtede træk\nmed større kraft.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00383" index="383">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren efterligner den\nflytning, der blev brugt umiddelbart\nfør den. Flytningen\nmislykkes, hvis intet andet træk\ner blevet brugt endnu.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00384" index="384">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren bruger sin\npsykiske kraft til at\nskifte ændringer til\nits Attack og\nSp. Atk med fjenden.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00385" index="385">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren anvender sin\npsykiske kraft til at\nskifte ændringer til\nits Forsvar og\nSp. Def med fjenden.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00386" index="386">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Dette angrebs kraft\nstiger jo mere\nfjenden har drevet\nop med statistiske ændringer.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00387" index="387">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Dette træk kan kun bruges\n efter at brugeren\nhar brugt alle de\andre træk, den kender\ni kampen.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00388" index="388">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Et frø, der forårsager\nbekymring, bliver plantet på\nfjenden. Det forhindrer\nsøvn ved at gøre dets\nevne Søvnløshed.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00389" index="389">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Dette træk gør det muligt for\brugeren at angribe først.\nDet mislykkes dog, hvis fjenden\nikke er klar til et\angreb.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00390" index="390">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren lægger en fælde\naf giftspidser ved\nfjendens fødder. De\nforgifter fjender, der\nskifter ind i kamp.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00391" index="391">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren bruger sin\npsykiske kraft til at\nskifte statændringer\nmed fjenden.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00392" index="392">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user envelops\nitself in a veil made\nof water. It regains\nsome HP on every\nturn.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00393" index="393">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user levitates\nusing electrically\ngenerated magnetism\nfor five turns.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00394" index="394">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren klæder sig\n ind i ild og\nlader mod fjenden.\nBrugeren lider også\nalvorlig skade.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00395" index="395">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The foe is attacked\nwith a shock wave.\nIt may also leave the\ntarget paralyzed.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00396" index="396">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user looses a\nblast of aura power\nfrom deep within its\nbody. This move is\ncertain to hit.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00397" index="397">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user polishes its\nbody to reduce drag.\nIt can sharply raise\nthe Speed stat.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00398" index="398">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Fjenden bliver stukket\nmed en fangarm eller\narm gennemsyret af\ngift. Det kan også\nforgifte fjenden.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00399" index="399">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user releases a\nhorrible aura imbued\nwith dark thoughts.\nIt may also make the\ntarget flinch.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00400" index="400">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren skråstreger den\nfjende i det øjeblik en\nmulighed opstår.\nDen har et højt\nkritisk hit-forhold.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00401" index="401">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user attacks by\nswinging its tail as if\nit were a vicious wave\nin a raging storm.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00402" index="402">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren smækker en\nspærreild af hård-\nskallede frø\nned på fjenden\nfra oven.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00403" index="403">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren angriber med\n luft, der skærer selv himlen.\nDet kan også få\nmålet til at vige.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00404" index="404">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user slashes at\nthe foe by crossing\nits scythes or claws\nas if they were a pair\nof scissors.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00405" index="405">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user vibrates its\nwings to generate a\ndamaging sound wave.\nIt may also lower the\nfoe’s Sp. Def stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00406" index="406">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The foe is attacked\nwith a shock wave\ngenerated by the\nuser’s gaping mouth.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00407" index="407">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user tackles the\nfoe while exhibiting\noverwhelming menace.\nIt may also make the\ntarget flinch.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00408" index="408">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren angriber med\n lysstråle, der\nglitter, som om den var\nlavet af ædelsten.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00409" index="409">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">En energi-drænende\npunch. Brugerens\nHP gendannes med\nhalvdelen af ​​skaden\naf målet.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00410" index="410">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user whirls its\nfists to send a wave\nof pure vacuum at\nthe foe. This move\nalways goes first.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00411" index="411">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user heightens\nits mental focus and\nunleashes its power.\nIt may also lower the\ntarget’s Sp. Def.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00412" index="412">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren henter strøm\nfra naturen og\nskyder den mod fjenden.\nDet kan også sænke\nmålets Sp. Def.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00413" index="413">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user tucks in\nits wings and charges\nfrom a low altitude.\nThe user also takes\nserious damage.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00414" index="414">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren får\njorden under fjenden\nerup med kraft.\nDet kan også sænke\nmålets Sp. Def.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00415" index="415">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren bytter holdt\nemner med fjenden\nhurtigere end øjet\nkan følge.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00416" index="416">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren lader på\nfjenden ved at bruge hver\nbit af dens magt.\nBrugeren skal hvile\nikke næste tur.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00417" index="417">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user stimulates\nits brain by thinking\nbad thoughts.\nIt sharply raises the\nuser’s Sp. Atk.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00418" index="418">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user strikes\nwith a tough punch as\nfast as a bullet.\nThis move always goes\nfirst.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00419" index="419">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Et angrebstræk, der\npåfører den dobbelte\ndaskade, hvis brugeren\ner blevet såret af\nfjenden i samme tur.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00420" index="420">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user flash\nfreezes chunks of\nice and hurls them.\nThis move always goes\nfirst.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00421" index="421">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user slashes with\na sharp claw made\nfrom shadows.\nIt has a high\ncritical-hit ratio.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00422" index="422">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user bites with\nelectrified fangs.\nIt may also make the\nfoe flinch or become\nparalyzed.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00423" index="423">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user bites with\ncold-infused fangs.\nIt may also make the\nfoe flinch or freeze.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00424" index="424">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user bites with\nflame-cloaked fangs.\nIt may also make the\nfoe flinch or sustain\na burn.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00425" index="425">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user extends its\nshadow and attacks\nthe foe from behind.\nThis move always goes\nfirst.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00426" index="426">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user launches a\nhard-packed mud ball\nto attack.\nIt may also lower the\ntarget’s accuracy.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00427" index="427">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user tears at\nthe foe with blades\nformed by psychic\npower. It has a high\ncritical-hit ratio.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00428" index="428">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren fokuserer sin\nviljestyrke til sit hoved\nog ramler fjenden.\nDet kan også få\nmålet til at vige.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00429" index="429">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user looses a\nflash of energy from\nits polished body.\nIt may also lower the\ntarget’s accuracy.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00430" index="430">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user gathers all\nits light energy and\nreleases it at once.\nIt may also lower the\nfoe’s Sp. Def stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00431" index="431">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A charging attack\nthat may also leave\nthe foe confused.\nIt can also be used\nto scale rocky walls.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00432" index="432">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Forhindringer flyttes,\nreducerer fjendens\nevasionsstatistik. Den kan\nogså bruges til at\nrydde dyb tåge osv.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00433" index="433">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user creates a\nbizarre area in which\nslower Pokémon get\nto move first for five\nturns.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00434" index="434">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Kometer tilkaldes\nned fra himlen.\nAngrebets rekyl\nreducerer\nbrugerens Sp. Atk stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00435" index="435">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A flare of electricity\nis loosed to strike\nall Pokémon in battle.\nIt may also cause\nparalysis.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00436" index="436">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">An inferno of scarlet\nflames washes over\nall Pokémon in battle.\nIt may also inflict\nburns.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00437" index="437">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A storm of sharp\nleaves is whipped up.\nThe attack’s recoil\nsharply reduces the\nuser’s Sp. Atk stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00438" index="438">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren hvirvler voldsomt\n med sine vinstokke eller\ntentakler for hårdt\n at slå fjenden.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00439" index="439">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user launches a\nhuge boulder at the\nfoe to attack.\nIt must rest on the\nnext turn, however.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00440" index="440">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">A slashing attack\nthat may also leave\nthe target poisoned.\nIt has a high\ncritical-hit ratio.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00441" index="441">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user shoots\nfilthy garbage at the\nfoe to attack.\nIt may also poison\nthe target.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00442" index="442">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The foe slams the\ntarget with its\nsteel-hard head.\nIt may also make the\ntarget flinch.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00443" index="443">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren affyrer en\nstålbombe, der\nklæber sig til målet.\nDette angreb vil\nikke gå glip af.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00444" index="444">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user stabs the\nfoe with a sharpened\nstone. It has a high\ncritical-hit ratio.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00445" index="445">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Hvis det er brugerens modsatte\n køn,\n charmeres fjenden\ntil kraftigt at sænke\nits Sp. Atk stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00446" index="446">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren lægger en fælde\naf svævende sten\nom fjenden. Fælden gør ondt på fjender, der\nskifter ind i kamp.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00447" index="447">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren fanger fjenden med græs og\nsnupper den. Jo tungere\nfjenden, jo større\nskaden.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00448" index="448">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren angriber\nved hjælp af en lydbølge\nbaseret på ord, den har\nlært. Det kan også\nforvirre fjenden.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00449" index="449">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren frigiver\nutallige billeder af\nlys. Dens type varierer\nafhængigt af den type plade\nbrugeren holder.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00450" index="450">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren bider fjenden. Hvis fjenden\nholder en bær, spiser\brugeren den og får dens effekt.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00451" index="451">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren affyrer et\nkoncentreret bundt\nelektricitet. Det kan\nogså hæve brugerens\nSp. Atk stat.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00452" index="452">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user slams its\nrugged body into the\nfoe to attack. The\nuser also sustains\nserious damage.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00453" index="453">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren kaster sig ud mod\nfjenden med en hastighed\nder gør den næsten\nusynlig. Den slår helt sikkert\nførst.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00454" index="454">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren råber ud\nunders for at\npuste fjenden.\nDen har et højt\nkritisk hit-forhold.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00455" index="455">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user calls out\nits underlings to\nmake a living shield,\nraising its Defense\nand Sp. Def stats.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00456" index="456">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren kalder\nits underlinger for at heale\nit. Brugeren genvinder\nop til halvdelen af ​​sin\nmaks. HP.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00457" index="457">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user delivers a\nlife-endangering head\nbutt at full power.\nThe user also takes\nterrible damage.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00458" index="458">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren smækker fjenden med en hale osv.\nMålet rammes\nto gange i træk.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00459" index="459">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren sprænger fjenden med kraft, der\nforvrænger lige tid.\nBrugeren skal hvile\n ikke næste tur.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00460" index="460">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user tears the\nfoe along with the\nspace around it.\nThis move has a high\ncritical-hit ratio.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00461" index="461">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren besvimer. Til gengæld vil den Pokémon, der indtager sin plads,\nfå sin status og\nHP fuldstændig gendannet.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00462" index="462">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Fjenden knuses\nmed stor kraft.\nAngrebet er mere\nkraftigt, jo mere HP\nfjenden har tilbage.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00463" index="463">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The foe becomes\ntrapped within a\nmaelstrom of fire\nthat rages for two\nto five turns.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00464" index="464">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Fjenden trækkes\nind i en verden af ​​totalt\ndmørke, der får den\n i søvn.\n</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00465" index="465">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">The user generates\na shock wave from\nwithin its body.\nIt may also lower the\ntarget’s Sp. Def.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00466" index="466">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren skaber et\ngust af frastødende\nvind. Det kan også\nhæve alle brugerens\nstatistik på én gang.</language>
	</row>
	<row id="narc_0587_00467" index="467">
		<attribute name="window_context_name">used</attribute>
		<language name="English">Brugeren forsvinder,\nså rammer fjenden\nden anden omgang.\nDet rammer, selvom\nfjenden brugte Protect.</language>
	</row>
</body>
